{"tid":591180,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一日內4宗老爆 竊匪攻陷跑馬地","createTime":"2018-03-13T09:53:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-13T11:14:05.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"af8c022df164cfb21042679e9a16982cd17efa9e","tid":591180,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T09:53:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180313/20330542\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180313%2F20330542&d=pBSnc7Ak3Aq9zpuZKNn22ttKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=3fe0f990\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180313%2F20330542&h=dbe6cd67\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180313/20330542</a><br />\n<br />\n一日內4宗老爆<br />\n竊匪攻陷跑馬地<br />\n<br />\n港聞   <br />\n         <br />\n【本報訊】繼跑馬地山光苑三單位連環失竊後，同區另一幢雲地利大廈一個單位，戶主夫婦前晚外出晚飯3小時，深夜返家即發現家中失竊，損失約30萬元財物，警方經調查後列為爆竊，交灣仔警區刑事調查隊追查是否同一幫竊賊所為。<br />\n<br />\n現場為跑馬地雲地利大廈一個低層單位。據知男戶主為68歲姓鍾男子，資料顯示他為資深會計師，曾經是羅兵咸永道會計師事務所的合夥人，並於2005年6月退休，同年9月與妻子聯名以628萬元購入上址單位。<br />\n<br />\n前晚7時許，鍾與妻子一同外出晚膳，至晚上10時許返家時，發現家中凌亂一片，立即報警。警方到場調查，鍾經點算後證實失竊價值25萬元珠寶及約5萬元現金，初步調查相信賊人撬窗潛入房間搜掠，警方列爆竊交灣仔刑事調查隊跟進。"},{"pid":"5f4756f8ff7ae3f9383683da8fd00b29d4240c36","tid":591180,"uid":74262,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T09:57:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b2b828e816469fc493a7c684630607d50b02f7f2","tid":591180,"uid":12021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T10:08:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"940a99cc2a8a257bf0ddf018e0827cc136cdeefd","tid":591180,"uid":56690,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T10:10:00.000Z","msg":"貧富懸殊減少 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cbc2d987e70855400830a329e840ce1a5cbfc8d","tid":591180,"uid":134226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T10:18:44.000Z","msg":"628萬買跑馬地<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今時今日600萬連一手私樓都冇得你買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f54cc60575c20c28b2ee8fc22256d5391f95a55f","tid":591180,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T11:14:05.000Z","msg":"引入專才"}]}